# On-Demand Games with Chainlink Custom Logic Automation

## Perfect for Your On-Demand Use Case!

**Your Game Flow:**
- ✅ Games start **when you want** (on-demand)
- ✅ Each game lasts exactly 5 minutes (10 songs × 10 sec × 3 rounds)
- ✅ Games can start at ANY time (3:17 PM, 7:42 PM, etc.)
- ✅ Automatic finalization via Chainlink when game ends

**Why Custom Logic is Perfect:**
- Monitors YOUR contract state (not the clock)
- Finalizes games whenever they end (regardless of time)
- Works for unpredictable start times
- Only triggers when YOUR conditions are met

## On-Demand Game Flow

```
Step 1: You (owner) call createGame()
        ↓
        Game starts NOW (e.g., 3:17:23 PM)
        endTime = NOW + 5 minutes (3:22:23 PM)
        
Step 2: Players enter during 5-minute window
        ↓
        Players pay 1 USDC each to join
        
Step 3: Game ends at 3:22:23 PM
        ↓
        Your backend calculates scores
        
Step 4: Your backend calls submitRankings()
        ↓
        Contract sets rankingsSubmitted = true
        
Step 5: Chainlink Automation detects via checkUpkeep
        ↓
        Within ~30 seconds, Chainlink calls performUpkeep
        
Step 6: Game finalized! Players claim prizes
```

