## How It Works

### Chainlink's Monitoring Loop

```javascript
// Chainlink nodes continuously run (every ~10-15 seconds):

checkUpkeep() → {
    Is there a current game?
    Has the game ended? (block.timestamp >= endTime)
    Have rankings been submitted?
    Is the game not finalized yet?
    
    IF ALL TRUE:
        return (true, gameId)
    ELSE:
        return (false, "")
}

// When checkUpkeep returns true:
performUpkeep(gameId) → {
    Finalize the game ✅
}
```

### Your Contract's Logic

```solidity
function checkUpkeep(bytes calldata)
    external view returns (bool, bytes memory)
{
    Game storage game = games[currentGameId];
    
    // Check if game is ready to finalize
    if (game.isActive && 
        block.timestamp >= game.endTime && 
        game.rankingsSubmitted && 
        !game.isFinalized) {
        
        return (true, abi.encode(currentGameId));
    }
    
    return (false, "");
}
```

