## Troubleshooting Common Issues

### 1. Game Not Finalizing
```javascript
// Check if rankings were submitted
const gameInfo = await contract.getGameInfo(gameId);
if (!gameInfo.rankingsSubmitted) {
    console.log("Issue: Rankings not submitted");
    // Submit rankings manually
    await contract.submitRankings(gameId, rankedPlayers);
}

// Check if Chainlink upkeep is working
const isReady = await contract.isGameReadyToFinalize(gameId);
if (isReady) {
    console.log("Game ready but not finalized - Chainlink issue");
    // Use manual finalization as backup
    await contract.manuallyFinalizeGame(gameId);
}
```

### 2. Players Can't Enter Game
```javascript
// Check game state
const gameInfo = await contract.getGameInfo(currentGameId);
if (!gameInfo.isActive) {
    console.log("Game not active");
}

// Check if game has ended
const timeRemaining = await contract.getTimeRemaining();
if (timeRemaining === 0) {
    console.log("Game has ended");
}

// Check player has sufficient USDC
const usdcBalance = await usdc.balanceOf(playerAddress);
if (usdcBalance < ENTRY_FEE) {
    console.log("Insufficient USDC balance");
}
```

### 3. Prize Claiming Issues
```javascript
// Check if game is finalized
const gameInfo = await contract.getGameInfo(gameId);
if (!gameInfo.isFinalized) {
    console.log("Game not finalized yet");
}

// Check if player was ranked
const ranking = await contract.getPlayerRanking(gameId, playerAddress);
if (ranking === 0) {
    console.log("Player was not ranked");
}

// Check if already claimed
const hasClaimed = await contract.hasPlayerClaimed(gameId, playerAddress);
if (hasClaimed) {
    console.log("Prize already claimed");
}
```

